# Data Preprocessing Report

## Dataset
Titanic Dataset

## Preprocessing Steps

1. Loaded the dataset using Pandas.
2. Checked missing values.
3. Filled missing Age values using Median.
4. Filled missing Embarked values using Mode.
5. Filled missing Fare values using Median.
6. Replaced missing Cabin values with "Unknown".
7. Encoded categorical columns.
8. Applied StandardScaler to numerical features.
9. Created a new feature called FamilySize.
10. Split the dataset into training and testing sets.
11. Exported the cleaned dataset as processed_dataset.csv.

## Conclusion
The dataset has been cleaned, transformed, and is ready for machine learning.
